    <p class="Neymar History">His actual name is Neymar da Silva Santos Jr. but his nickname is Neymar which is what everyone calls him. He was born on February 5, 1992 in Mogi das Cruzes, Sao Paulo, Brazil. He joined the youth system of Santos FC at age 11 and was eventually offered a chance to develp at Real Madrid C.F. at age 14 but he decided to stay. He made his senior debut in 2009 and earned Best Young Player award that year. in 2011 he led his team to its first Copa Libertadores championship in 48 years and produced the FIFA Goal of the Year. in 2012 he scored his 100th goal on his birthday. In May 2013, he transferred to FC Barcelona.
